com.canoo.dolphin.impl

Class AbstractBeanBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.canoo.dolphin.impl.AbstractBeanBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeanBuilder

    public abstract class AbstractBeanBuilder
extends Object
implements BeanBuilder
    A BeanBuilder is responsible for building a Dolphin Bean that is specified as a class. The main (and only public) method is create(Class), which expects the Class of the Dolphin Bean and returns the generated Bean. The generated Dolphin Bean will be registered in the BeanRepositoryImpl.
